# AMR D convergence Couette, scale 1 source template.

Simulation amr_d_couette_scale1 D2Q9

Define scale = 1
Define U = 0.04
Define omega = 1.0
Define rho0 = 1.0

Domain L = 18 x 14  N = 18 x 14
Physics nu = 0.16666666666666666

Boundary west periodic
Boundary east periodic
Boundary south wall
Boundary north velocity(ux = 0.04, uy = 0)

Refine yband { region = [0, 4, 18, 10], ratio = 2 }

Run 80 steps
Diagnostics every 20 [step, ux, uy]
